Segments: l ó/o + s á/a + s ɛ̀/ɛ ʔ
Graphemes: ^ l ó = s á - s ɛ̀ ʔ $

Segments: p w á/a iʰ/i /h + t r ʋ̀/ʋ
Graphemes: ^ p w á iʰ - t r ʋ̀ $

Segments: s ě/e i n + b ē/e i
Graphemes: ^ s ě i n = b ē i $

Segments: θ ǝ̂/ə ŋ + p ê/e ŋ
Graphemes: ^ θ ǝ̂ ŋ = p ê ŋ $

Segments: ɕ ū/u ɓ á/a + pʰ ō/o
Graphemes: ^ ɕ ū ɓ á - pʰ ō $

Segments: tʰ ú/u + t è/e + p è/e
Graphemes: ^ tʰ ú - t è - p è $

Segments: ǝ̄/ə + θ í/i + p à/a ʔ
Graphemes: ^ ǝ̄ = θ í - p à ʔ $

Segments: ʃ w é/e ʔ + m̥ è/e ʔ
Graphemes: ^ š w é ʔ - m̥ è ʔ $

Segments: + ɕ ū/u + θ ǝ́/ə + m ī/i
Graphemes: ^ = ɕ ū = θ ǝ́ = m ī $

Segments: s ù/u + θ í/i + m ì/i ʔ
Graphemes: ^ s ù = θ í = m ì ʔ $

Segments: k ə + n ɔ̄/ɔ + b ȁ/a
Graphemes: ^ k ǝ = n ɔ̄ = b ȁ $

Segments: kʰ ɔ́/ɔ + m ù/u + b é/e
Graphemes: ^ kʰ ɔ́ = m ù = b é $

Segments: dʒ ɯ̄/ɯ + θ ì/i + m ì/i
Graphemes: ^ ǯ ɯ̄ = θ ì = m ì $

Segments: dʒ á/a u + m ē/e i n
Graphemes: ^ ǯ á u = m ē i n $

Segments: d ɛ̀/ɛ + t ǝ̄/ə ɓ ò/o ʔ
Graphemes: ^ d ɛ̀ = t ǝ̄ ɓ ò ʔ $

Segments: p ò/o + ʔ ó/o + l ù/u
Graphemes: ^ p ò = ʔ ó = l ù $

Segments: k á/a + ʔ ɯ̀/ɯ + t ɤ́/ɤ
Graphemes: ^ k á = ʔ ɯ̀ - t ɤ́ $

Segments: k ā/a n + ʔ ú/u ŋ
Graphemes: ^ k ā n = ʔ ú ŋ $

Segments: ʔ à/a + t ò/o + kʰ l ó/o
Graphemes: ^ ʔ à = t ò = kʰ l ó $

Segments: ʔ à/a + t à/a + k l ū/u
Graphemes: ^ ʔ à = t à = k l ū $

Segments: tʰ w ē/e i + k l ɔ̀/ɔ
Graphemes: ^ tʰ w ē i - k l ɔ̀ $
